race.comment: BUTTER BING (2) ran a good time (19.23) winning a Grade 5 two back at this track but missed the frame latest finishing sixth at Richmond Straight. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. HUMBLE TIGRESS (3) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at Goulburn over 350m behind Goodbye Mate (20.51) in a Grade 5. Placed at her previous run. Key runner on best form. CHARING CROSS (1) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at Richmond Straight over 324m behind Ruination (18.08) in a NG. Has ability and can measure up. DUCHESS DOLLY (8) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish at a big quote.
